{"tid":2246940,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"向台北保護傘餐廳潑糞男子 台北地院批准羈押禁見 台北警方另逮捕3人 疑涉嫌教唆犯案","createTime":"2020-10-17T12:54:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-18T02:11:14.000Z","uid":292499,"like":108,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"3f703cb4f64e147a1e05b7088e565433e352497a","tid":2246940,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T12:54:23.000Z","msg":"......<br />\n<br />\n北檢認為，莫男對案情的說明仍有部份待釐清，此時若放他回社會，有高度串證與逃亡的可能性，且不排除反覆實施犯罪，不利證據保存，影響案件偵辦，訊後決定聲押禁見，卷宗移交北院，北院火速於17日晚間8時召開羈押庭審理，8點半即裁准。<br />\n<br />\n另外，莫男經檢察官曉以大義，承認以一次一萬五的代價，朝「保護傘」潑灑穢物，警方目前已追到他的上手，也就是其江姓高中同學及一對表兄弟，正在進行警詢中，至於三人背後是否另有藏鏡人，仍待突破。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/3324548\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F3324548&d=6FpmejEDNbHOA1ae24haowxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=c585f2a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F3324548&h=b390df53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/3324548</a>"},{"pid":"9941e069a955efcd28df496efaf02aeb2ec7c519","tid":2246940,"uid":274532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T12:54:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b092780e033ad14ce885aa0038a67f3d5fd414b","tid":2246940,"uid":72466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T12:55:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e0bb154d75c2d03b74c8f69b1217cea6c8582e3","tid":2246940,"uid":4574,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T12:56:48.000Z","msg":"間諜罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8d9c736271d9f7b40592c94603b9e6a0af75be6","tid":22